the INNER JOIN is keyword That return the Values that are matched ih the table
It Do not return the unmatched values form the  tables 
We can use Mutiple INNER JOIN keyword in the single Querry of the MYsql optimizer handle it efficeintly 

QUERRY :
 Select COL_1 , COL_2 from Table_1 INNER JOIN Table_2 ON Table_1.COL_1=Table_2.COL_2;

this querry will return the same record that consist both the table

PRO TIP for Consider RIGHT Table And Left Table

FROM -----> LEFT table
INNER JOIN ------> RIGHT Table
